      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:29:2",
      "text": [
        " قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) الرَّجُلُ يَقْذِفُ امْرَأَتَهُ قَبْلَ أَنْ يَدْخُلَ بِهَا قَالَ يُضْرَبُ الْحَدَّ وَ يُخَلَّى بَيْنَهُ وَ بَيْنَهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, form his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from one of his companions who said, ",
          "‘I said to Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, ‘The man accuses his wife before he copulates with her. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He would be whipped the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), and there would be separation between him and her’."
        ]
      }
    }
